Dialogue: 1,0:23:46.16,0:23:51.16,ED2-JP,,0,0,0,,夢のはじまりの合図が鳴る
Comment: 1,0:22:31.66,0:22:35.13,ED2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,480)}I’ll always believe tomorrow
